To set up a build environment from this repository, run:

$./autogen.sh

or

$NOCONFIGURE=1 ./autogen.sh

or to update the gnulib to the latest files then

git clone https://git.savannah.gnu.org/gnulib.git

change to tmpwatch directory
run [gnulib] directory/gnulib/gnulib-tool --import

then ./autogen.sh as above.
